		<title>AI 選股正夯！散戶用 ChatGPT 選股 市場六年將增六倍</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/09/25/ai-%e9%81%b8%e8%82%a1%e6%ad%a3%e5%a4%af%ef%bc%81%e6%95%a3%e6%88%b6%e7%94%a8-chatgpt-%e9%81%b8%e8%82%a1-%e5%b8%82%e5%a0%b4%e5%85%ad%e5%b9%b4%e5%b0%87%e5%a2%9e%e5%85%ad%e5%80%8d/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報 時事新聞]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Thu, 25 Sep 2025 10:39:51 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[時事]]></category>
